      },
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent verification against canonical benchmarks is documented in the ANSYS Fluent Verification Manual (Release 2022R2). Taylor-Couette and lid-driven cavity benchmark results confirm correct implementation of the k-omega SST turbulence model used in this study."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/factor/morrison-cou1-disc-error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
